parameters:
Thank goodness, the general is going to bid for
you. That person will take good care of you, you
know?

properly so there won't be any complaints.

How's the taste of the Empire's special

pump it directly into your brain.

Oh... As expected of the Resistance's cyborg, then
next is this one.

Good, you're the Empire's obedient female pig!
I'll make sure you understand that well.
Aaaaaah! No, no! I'm not a female pig!

Isn't that wrong? You're a female pig who only has
dicks on her mind!

Hehehe... Quite stubborn, aren't you... Next is
this one.

Aaaaaah!? What is this!? So many dicks...⁉ Stop
it! Don't show me such things!

Images are streamed directly into Esuka's brain
through the visor that's been attached to her.

Hyahaha! I'm projecting it directly onto your
retina, I'll make sure you can only think about
dicks, so give up!

Aaaaaah! Help me! My mind is getting all messed up
by dicks...!
No good, I'll continue until you become obedient~

I'm going to thoroughly train your body so that
you won't be embarrassed no matter where you go as
a female pig, be grateful!
Nooooo! I don't want the dicks!

Good, it seems to be going smoothly. Hey, you, try
saying something.

Aaah... I... I'm the Empire's... obedient female
pig...

Alright, make sure to serve your master's dick
properly!
Dick! Dick! Please give me dick! Dick! Dick!

Hyahaha! It seems your brain has completely become
an erogenous zone... It's about time to ship you
out, the customers are eagerly waiting.

The final touch... You are the property of the
Empire until you die!

The Imperial Army takes out a branding machine.
This brand is something the Imperial Army uses on
prisoners and such, it contains nanomachines,
which can immediately identify the location, and
can also cause a very small explosion with the
push of a button.
Swear your loyalty properly, you female pig~

Nnnooo... I swear... I pledge my loyalty to the
Empire...

Hehehe... With this, the customers should be
satisfied.
